##### Make sure we can put emojis into the source code.
AddCharset utf-8 .js

##### Set the 404 page to the home page, so all requests return the index,
#####  except if they lead to a real file on the server.
ErrorDocument 404 /index.html

##### Deal with fetches directly to this document, which always have status 403 in Apache.
ErrorDocument 403 /index.html

##### Prevent Apache from generating a separate index page for requests to folders.
##### It is only needed if there are real subfolders on the server.
Options -Indexes